  "title": "Blog-Short term Renting, AirBnB(Chinese)",
  "slug": "blog-short-term-renting-airbnbchinese",
  "rawHTML": "<p>在美国夏威夷做民宿能赚多少？</p>\t\t\n\t\t<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">在美国投资房产时，您可以选择长期租赁或者像Airbnb这样的短期租赁方式。东部雪场20万买的房子，首付只付了5万，年净利润率有将近2.6万？夏威夷Waikiki Beach 21万买的房子，装修3万。共花24万，年利润率高达3.6万？在Joshua Tree 国家公园85万买的豪宅做Airbnb，不赚钱？</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">今天我们就来聊一聊在美国不同地区做民宿的收益。</p><p>发表于：9/27/2022</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/pexels-cottonbro-5077042-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/pexels-cottonbro-5077042-scaled.jpg 1707w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/pexels-cottonbro-5077042-200x300.jpg 200w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/pexels-cottonbro-5077042-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/pexels-cottonbro-5077042-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/pexels-cottonbro-5077042-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/pexels-cottonbro-5077042-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/pexels-cottonbro-5077042-400x600.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEnvelope\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M464 64H48C21.49 64 0 85.49 0 112v288c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h416c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48V112c0-26.51-21.49-48-48-48zm0 48v40.805c-22.422 18.259-58.168 46.651-134.587 106.49-16.841 13.247-50.201 45.072-73.413 44.701-23.208.375-56.579-31.459-73.413-44.701C106.18 199.465 70.425 171.067 48 152.805V112h416zM48 400V214.398c22.914 18.251 55.409 43.862 104.938 82.646 21.857 17.205 60.134 55.186 103.062 54.955 42.717.231 80.509-37.199 103.053-54.947 49.528-38.783 82.032-64.401 104.947-82.653V400H48z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tExternal-link-square-alt\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M448 80v352c0 26.51-21.49 48-48 48H48c-26.51 0-48-21.49-48-48V80c0-26.51 21.49-48 48-48h352c26.51 0 48 21.49 48 48zm-88 16H248.029c-21.313 0-32.08 25.861-16.971 40.971l31.984 31.987L67.515 364.485c-4.686 4.686-4.686 12.284 0 16.971l31.029 31.029c4.687 4.686 12.285 4.686 16.971 0l195.526-195.526 31.988 31.991C358.058 263.977 384 253.425 384 231.979V120c0-13.255-10.745-24-24-24z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tFacebook-f\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M279.14 288l14.22-92.66h-88.91v-60.13c0-25.35 12.42-50.06 52.24-50.06h40.42V6.26S260.43 0 225.36 0c-73.22 0-121.08 44.38-121.08 124.72v70.62H22.89V288h81.39v224h100.17V288z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tLinkedin-in\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M100.28 448H7.4V148.9h92.88zM53.79 108.1C24.09 108.1 0 83.5 0 53.8a53.79 53.79 0 0 1 107.58 0c0 29.7-24.1 54.3-53.79 54.3zM447.9 448h-92.68V302.4c0-34.7-.7-79.2-48.29-79.2-48.29 0-55.69 37.7-55.69 76.7V448h-92.78V148.9h89.08v40.8h1.3c12.4-23.5 42.69-48.3 87.88-48.3 94 0 111.28 61.9 111.28 142.3V448z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tTwitter\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M459.37 151.716c.325 4.548.325 9.097.325 13.645 0 138.72-105.583 298.558-298.558 298.558-59.452 0-114.68-17.219-161.137-47.106 8.447.974 16.568 1.299 25.34 1.299 49.055 0 94.213-16.568 130.274-44.832-46.132-.975-84.792-31.188-98.112-72.772 6.498.974 12.995 1.624 19.818 1.624 9.421 0 18.843-1.3 27.614-3.573-48.081-9.747-84.143-51.98-84.143-102.985v-1.299c13.969 7.797 30.214 12.67 47.431 13.319-28.264-18.843-46.781-51.005-46.781-87.391 0-19.492 5.197-37.36 14.294-52.954 51.655 63.675 129.3 105.258 216.365 109.807-1.624-7.797-2.599-15.918-2.599-24.04 0-57.828 46.782-104.934 104.934-104.934 30.213 0 57.502 12.67 76.67 33.137 23.715-4.548 46.456-13.32 66.599-25.34-7.798 24.366-24.366 44.833-46.132 57.827 21.117-2.273 41.584-8.122 60.426-16.243-14.292 20.791-32.161 39.308-52.628 54.253z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t本文将讨论：\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#3rK4yIV7\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t夏威夷民宿\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#PDgewcnh\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t东部雪场民宿\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t加州国家公园Joshua Tree民宿\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t<p><strong>夏威夷 Wakiki Beach Studio Condotel</strong></p><p>地理位置：走路到Wakiki Beach主街购物中心只要5分钟。</p><ul><li>大小：1卧室 + 1个沙发床</li><li>买入价：21万美金全现金买（2021年买的，目前房价35万+）<br />买入时间：2021年中左右</li><li>是否装修：是</li><li>装修花销：大约3万美金</li><li>总投入：24万美金</li></ul><p>现在来看一下这套夏威夷投资房的月ROI：</p><p>扣除税、清洁费、物业费和管理费，目前的年现金流是$36,000</p><p>回报率：$36,000 / $240,000 = 15%</p><p><strong>注：</strong>Airbnb Payout: Airbnb 扣除平台费用后直接付给你的钱</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1362\" height=\"910\" src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hawaii.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hawaii.png 1362w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hawaii-300x200.png 300w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hawaii-1024x684.png 1024w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hawaii-768x513.png 768w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/hawaii-600x401.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1362px) 100vw, 1362px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p><strong>东部Okemo 雪场</strong></p><ul><li>地理位置：Okemo Mountain 雪场入口处</li><li>大小：1卧室 + 1个沙发床</li><li>买入价：20万美金。约25%，即5万首付 (2020年购买，目前房价30万+)</li><li>是否做了装修：否</li><li>买入时间：2020年</li><li>其他支出：1万美金</li><li>总投入：6万美金</li></ul><p>现在来看一下这套雪场投资房的月ROI：<br /><br /></p><p><strong>冬季</strong></p><p>但这还不够！第二步是要满足以下条件中的任意一种：</p><ul><li>平均租期少于7天</li><li>平均租期少于30天，且提供实质性服务</li></ul><p>如果您选择通过Airbnb或VRBO平台进行短期租赁，建议将租期设定为少于7天，以增加税务上的安全边际。</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1362\" height=\"942\" src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/winter.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/winter.png 1362w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/winter-300x207.png 300w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/winter-1024x708.png 1024w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/winter-768x531.png 768w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/winter-600x415.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1362px) 100vw, 1362px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1334\" height=\"738\" src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sumer.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sumer.png 1334w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sumer-300x166.png 300w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sumer-1024x567.png 1024w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sumer-768x425.png 768w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sumer-600x332.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1334px) 100vw, 1334px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p><strong>支出</strong></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"950\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/expense.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/expense.png 950w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/expense-300x152.png 300w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/expense-768x388.png 768w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/expense-600x303.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 950px) 100vw, 950px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p><strong>年净利润</strong></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1354\" height=\"574\" src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/profit.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/profit.png 1354w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/profit-300x127.png 300w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/profit-1024x434.png 1024w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/profit-768x326.png 768w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/profit-600x254.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1354px) 100vw, 1354px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p>由于这套房子有贷款，所以每个月月供为 $890.</p><p>因此，现在的年现金流为：</p><p>$36800 - $890*12 = $26,120</p><p>回报率：$26,120 / $70,000 = 37%</p><p>考虑到这个雪场的房子只是付了首付，而前面介绍的夏威夷的房子为全现金。为了方便比较，我们假设雪场的房子也是全现金买，那么东部雪场这套房子的假设花销则为21万（20万现金+ 1万其他支出）</p><p>另外，一个很重要的区别在于，这个雪场的房子没有扣除Property Manager(PM)费用。原因是这个房子的主人自己管理，所以算是省了一笔开销。在该地区PM的费用占平台payoff的35%。所以这样计算一下，PM费用是17,500也是一笔不小的开销。</p><p>若扣除PM费用，年回报率为</p><p>($26,120 + 890*12 - 17,500)/$210,000 = 9.1% </p><p>这样对比下来，夏威夷的房产短租回报比更高，且夏威夷的房子同样价格面积会小一些。</p><p><strong>加州国家公园Joshua Tree</strong></p><p>地理位置：Joshua Tree 国家公园入口处</p><p>大小：3卧室3卫浴间，住 6-10人不成问题<br />买入价：85万美金 (目前redfin估价 95万+), 首付约40%，即~34万美金</p><p>是否做了装修：否</p><p>买入时间：2021年</p><p>现在来看一下这套民宿的月ROI：</p><p>Aribnb Payout: 平均$6000/month </p><p>PM Fee：总收入的 25% -- 大约$1500</p><p>水电: $1000/month</p><p>根据投资人透露，</p><ul><li>Joshua Tree的季节性很强，7，8月份沙漠非常热，收入就不是很好，但是冬天又很不错。</li><li>管理费用非常高 （25%），水电费用高，因为沙漠昼夜温差大，从早到晚都要开空调。</li><li>来Joshua Tree旅游的人，一般是road trip，最多在那里住几天。而不是想去夏威夷度假一样，住上一周。因此需要经常需要清扫，这样的话就又增加了维护成本.</li><li>扣除掉上述管理费，水电费，清洁费，基本收支平衡，很难盈利</li></ul><p><em><strong>免责申明</strong></em></p><p><em><b> </b>本文及其中任何文字均仅为一般性的介绍，绝不构成任何法律意见或建议，不得作为法律意见或建议以任何形式被依赖。任何投资都有风险，包括可能的本金损失。投资策略例如分散投资或再平衡，并不能保证更好的表现，也无法消除投资损失的风险。</em></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<figure><img src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/shutterstock_2176795857_1140x855-e1719437535911-qq8vk1h7g8p6joer5dihw9y6xpl1dq2bl942ny0crc.jpg\" title=\"shutterstock_2176795857.jpg_1140x855\" alt=\"shutterstock_2176795857.jpg_1140x855\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><h2>高利率如何影响我们的财务决策</h2><p>全文</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<figure><img src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/image_0-3-e1719444732274-qqhqgmgl5gr2i080lx4y56vwsb93mz6kov1qdzmv88.webp\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><h2>高利率下的投资选择</h2><p>全文</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<figure><a href=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/blog-private-equitychinese/\" tabindex=\"-1\"><img src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/pexels-spacex-23764-scaled-qr9l42sq40pgblk8idn5mmni8dcskfmrcrrp1cjno8.jpg\" title=\"pexels-spacex-23764\" alt=\"pexels-spacex-23764\" loading=\"lazy\" /></a></figure><h2><a href=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/blog-private-equitychinese/\">如何投资SpaceX这类未上市公司？</a></h2><p>全文</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<figure><img src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/17_201601022235041044B-qql00762c7gjd7mg6jimmv8yi0cux58qt7qupbfpnc.gif\" title=\"17_201601022235041044B\" alt=\"17_201601022235041044B\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><h2>金钱和爱情</h2><p>全文</p>",
